OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777532747
OL,3,CBarrister fined after turning up drunk
OL,4,Cto represent client in court
OL,6,FA barrister who collapsed in a Kent
OL,7,Fcourt due to alcohol intoxication,
OL,8,Fwhilst he was there to represent a
OL,9,Fclient, has been fined by the
OL,10,Fregulator.
OL,12,FJames Hankinson turned up drunk to
OL,13,FMaidstone Combined Court in March
OL,14,F2025, forcing his clients case to be
OL,15,Fadjourned.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
