FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777532747
OL,3,CBarrister fined after turning up drunk
OL,4,Cto represent client in court
OL,6,FThe barrister supplied toxicology test
OL,7,Fto his legal chambers "to demonstrate
OL,8,Fhis ongoing abstinence from alcohol",
OL,9,Fand he was offered support for a
OL,10,Fphased return to work ` including
OL,11,F"checks to ensure he does not consume
OL,12,Falcohol when at court or when dealing
OL,13,Fwith clients".
